name: AVAXWARRIORS
description:
In 2077 Alfa created 8,888 cloned versions of her consciousness. They
were each placed into a robotic suit that the conscious could control.
In essence, each Warrior is Alfa. They work to her regime, order and
demands. Their mission is to defend Alfa at all costs and to further the
knowledge and evolution of the human species. Alfa has stated that only
8,888 AVAXWARRIORS will be created. They will all be unique 1 of 1's.
